description: Number of partitions of n into parts not of the form 21k, 21k+6 or 21k-6. Also number of partitions with at most 5 parts of size 1 and differences between parts at distance 9 are greater than 1.
references: G. E. Andrews, The Theory of Partitions, Addison-Wesley, 1976, p. 109.
